      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，NeedMore需要支持自循环——当收到more input时继续留在NeedMore，直到输入结束。另外要有两条出路：正常结束走Complete，遇到异常走Error。",
      "elements_involved": [
